title: Olena Rodina
text: Olena Rodina (born 17 May 1975) is a Ukrainian <a href="Cross-country%20skiing%20%28sport%29">cross-country skier</a>. She competed in <a href="Cross-country%20skiing%20at%20the%202002%20Winter%20Olympics">three events</a> at the <a href="2002%20Winter%20Olympics">2002 Winter Olympics</a>.
